    <item>
      <title>卢旺达总统有望以 99% 的得票率获得第四个任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/rwanda-s-president-is-set-to-secure-fourth-term-with-99-of-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卢旺达总统保罗·卡加梅在已统计的五分之四选票中赢得 99% 的选票，获得又一个五年任期，延续其对这个东非国家二十五年的统治。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/rwanda-s-president-is-set-to-secure-fourth-term-with-99-of-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:55:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜驻古巴高级外交官叛逃至韩国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/senior-north-korean-diplomat-based-in-cuba-defects-to-the-south</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜驻古巴的一名高级外交官于 11 月叛逃韩国，成为近年来离开这个封闭国家前往韩国的最高级别外交官之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/senior-north-korean-diplomat-based-in-cuba-defects-to-the-south</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 04:03:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普副总统候选人万斯称中国是美国“最大威胁”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/trump-s-vp-pick-vance-says-china-is-the-biggest-threat-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自被任命为唐纳德·特朗普的竞选搭档以来，JD 万斯在首次接受采访时将中国称为美国面临的最大威胁，并强调一旦当选，美国政府可能会对北京采取强硬立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/trump-s-vp-pick-vance-says-china-is-the-biggest-threat-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊隆·马斯克每月向亲特朗普超级政治行动委员会捐赠 4500 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/pro-trump-super-pac-backed-by-elon-musk-raises-8-8-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克承诺每月向支持唐纳德·特朗普的政治团体投入 4500 万美元，此举将为共和党候选人在 11 月大选前的连任竞选提供大量资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/pro-trump-super-pac-backed-by-elon-musk-raises-8-8-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 23:48:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟委员将缺席匈牙利会议讨论奥尔班外交问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/eu-commissioners-to-skip-hungary-s-meetings-over-orban-diplomacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为抗议欧盟总理维克托·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）对莫斯科和北京的外交访问，欧盟委员会将减少参加欧盟轮值主席国匈牙利计划举行的非正式会议的级别。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/eu-commissioners-to-skip-hungary-s-meetings-over-orban-diplomacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:44:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
